WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:01.666
Are you looking for me?

2
00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:04.833
What's wrong, husband?

3
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:07.533
I thought I heard you calling my name?

4
00:00:07.966 --> 00:00:09.166
Why are you here?

5
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.600
I've been outside all along

6
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.133
Shh

7
00:00:13.333 --> 00:00:14.566
It's me, Li Bei Qīng

8
00:00:14.966 --> 00:00:16.066
Li Bei Qīng?

9
00:00:16.466 --> 00:00:17.533
Here, eat this

10
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:19.766
Are you okay?

11
00:00:20.966 --> 00:00:21.866
I know

12
00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:23.700
Zhang Wen Xu and that secretary

13
00:00:23.866 --> 00:00:25.000
wanted to frame you

14
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:27.733
It was my carelessness

15
00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:29.566
that led me to fall into their trap

16
00:00:30.866 --> 00:00:32.400
If he has no regard

17
00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:33.566
for our years of marriage

18
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:35.933
he can't blame me for being ruthless

19
00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:37.133
What do you want to do?

20
00:00:39.366 --> 00:00:40.866
I want you to help me with something

21
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:42.333
I just had a bit to drink

22
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:43.200
and got a little tipsy

23
00:00:43.433 --> 00:00:44.933
so I came outside to get some fresh air

24
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:45.700
Weren't you

25
00:00:45.766 --> 00:00:47.166
just inside?

26
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:49.366
Is there someone inside?

27
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:51.666
Want to know who's inside?

28
00:00:52.166 --> 00:00:53.700
Why not open it and find out?

29
00:00:53.700 --> 00:00:55.133
I have the key right here

30
00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:01.700
Zhang Wen Xu, Jiang Yu Yong

31
00:01:02.466 --> 00:01:04.833
The pain I endured in my past life

32
00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:07.700
I want to return to you a thousand times over

33
00:01:08.700 --> 00:01:09.666
In this life

34
00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:11.966
it's your turn to go to hell